{
  "texts": [
    "Since we are interested in stellar Hα variability on time scales ranging from days to years, the stellar sources with too short T span scales are not preferred.",
    "In this work, we only employ the stellar sources with time span of multiple observations greater than three days (i.e., T span > 3 days).",
    "The stellar sources that do not meet this condition are removed from our sample.",
    "In the LAMOST MRS Parameter Catalog, the stellar atmospheric parameters T eff, log g, and [Fe/H] are provided for each of the observations (coadded spectra) of the same stellar source.",
    "Thus a time-domain object has multiple measurements of the stellar atmospheric parameters."
  ]
}